---
title: Annex Key Skip & Undead Dragon Skip
hidden: false
---
The **Annex Key Skip** allows the player to perform a precise jump that bypasses the need for the [Annex Key](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/annex-key); it is commonly used in [**All Achievements**](/ds1remaster/all-achievements) speedruns.

The **Undead Dragon Skip** allows the player to avoid fighting the [Undead Dragon](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/undead-dragon) and go directly to [**Priscilla** ](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/crossbreed-priscilla)instead.

